data.title: Charles Emmanuel, Prince of Carignano
data.meta_description: Charles Emmanuel of Savoy, 6th Prince of Carignano was a Prince of Savoy and later the Prince of Carignano between 1780 and 1800, and the paternal grandfather of Vittorio Emanuele II, the first king of a united Italy.
